Come see this charming home in the Woodcrest Community. This beautiful 4-bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home offers spacious living with modern amenities. The open layout is perfect for entertaining and family gatherings. This home has been meticulously cared for and is move-in ready. All stainless kitchen appliances convey with the house, making your move-in hassle free. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your new home. Schedule a viewing today!
